Test Case 1 — User Registration and Login

Test Case ID: TC-001
Module: Authentication
Tested By: Divyansh
Date: June 2026

Objective:
Verify that a new user can register and login successfully with role-based access.

Pre-conditions:


Application is running on http://localhost:5174
Backend is running on http://localhost:8000


Test Steps:


Open http://localhost:5174 in browser
Click "Create Profile" on login page
Enter Full Name: "Test User", Email: "test@smartrail.com", Password: "test123"
Click "Create Account"
Login with the registered credentials
Observe the dashboard and sidebar


Expected Result:


Account is created successfully
User is redirected to login page after registration
After login, only Passenger Mode is visible in sidebar
Admin Mode toggle is completely hidden
User name appears in top right corner


Actual Result:


Account created and stored in localStorage successfully
Redirected to login page after 1 second
Passenger Dashboard loaded with Passenger Mode only
Admin Mode hidden as expected
"Test User" displayed in top right corner


